      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a clean appearance with only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with careful use, and the interior is tidy and comfortable. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a smooth-running engine and a responsive transmission that make it a pleasure to drive. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that balances performance and value perfectly.",
