      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014honestly, it drives like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s clean, comfy, and ready for your next road trip. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
