    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 power plant. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate chassis fatigue. The 3.2L atmospheric engine breathes through six individual throttle bodies, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Performance is bolstered by a refreshed cooling system and Bilstein B6 dampers for optimal damping rates. While showing honest cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and suspension kinematics remain sharp, making this an ideal candidate for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
