    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic offers a refined driving experience for those who refuse to compromise on performance. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and small scuffs on the rear bumper consistent with daily use. Inside, the Agate Grey leather cabin is in excellent shape, with the bolsters showing minimal wear and the panoramic sunroof functioning perfectly. This vehicle features the Premium Package Plus, including heated and ventilated front seats and a crisp Bose Surround Sound system. Mechanically, it is robust; the 3.0L Twin-Turbo V6 runs smoothly, and the PDK transmission provides lightning-fast shifts. It has been serviced regularly at 10k-mile intervals with a full log of records included. It sits on 20-inch RS Spyder Design wheels wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a reliable, well-documented luxury SUV that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
